title Rate State Machine Diagram
!define PUMLOFFICIALSYNTAXCHECK
!define PUOFFICIALSYNTAXCHECK_CMD "plantuml --syntax-check"
!define PUOFFICIALSYNTAXCHECK_ARGS
!define PUOFFICIALSYNTAXCHECK_OPT "--offload"

title Rate State Machine Diagram

[*] --> Inactive

state Inactive
state Active
state Expired
state Archived

Inactive --> Active : startDateReached
Active --> Expired : finishDateReached
Expired --> Archived : oneYearPassed
Archived --> [*]


